软件包 prefuse.data.column

Data columns for storing typed data within a data table.

请参见：
          描述

接口摘要
Column Interface for a data column in a table.
 

类摘要
AbstractColumn Abstract base class for Column implementations.
BooleanColumn Column implementation storing boolean values.
ByteColumn Column implementation for storing int values.
ColumnFactory Factory class for generating appropriate column instances.
ColumnMetadata ColumnMetadata stores computed metadata and statistics for a singe column instance.
ConstantColumn Column implementation holding a single, constant value for all rows.
DateColumn Column implementation for storing Date values.
DoubleColumn Column implementation for storing double values.
ExpressionColumn Column instance that stores values provided by an Expression instance.
FloatColumn Column instance for sotring flaot values.
IntColumn Column implementation for storing int values.
LongColumn Column implementation for storing long values.
ObjectColumn Column implementation for storing arbitrary Object values.
 

软件包 prefuse.data.column 的描述

Data columns for storing typed data within a data table. In most cases, these classes should not be instantiated directly. Instead use the setColumn() methods of the Table class, which will call the appropriate ColumnFactory method for you.
